{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2b8e45caec","title":"应下决心在陕南分散游击","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7dfc2459e5","index":0,"year":1946,"month":7,"day":25,"articleId":"2b8e45caec"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji21.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji21":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"9330db8092","type":"paragraph","text":"应下决心在陕南分散游击","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"2b8e45caec"},{"id":"6ea676fb2c","type":"paragraph","text":"1946年7月25日）李、文、任各电器。（一）已电西安办事处周子健代表先念与三十二小组接治，声明愿意调处，要求政府军停止围追，以利谈判。（二）只要你们能生存，恢复谈判及实行停战是有希望的，因国民党对我中原军四出游击深为恐俱。（三）你们应下决心以团为单位分散于陕南名县，划分区域，每团管一县至二县，分散的程度以能打民团及国民党一连一营为标准。你们可开始分散于三四个县内，取得经验，然","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"2b8e45caec"},{"id":"ac146f5150","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"2b8e45caec"},{"id":"afc87e1a5e","type":"paragraph","text":"午有1]这是电泽东为中共中央起草的给中原军区司令员李先念、第二队司令员文建武和政治委员任质斌的电报。","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"2b8e45caec"}],"page":{"id":"cbee28318b","publicationId":"maoquanji21","articleId":"2b8e45caec","start":523,"end":523}}}},"__N_SSG":true}